column5: Well we finally tied the knot yesterday and now my long awaited trip to Temagami is a day away. Hopefully I can write up a report with tons of fish pics and not just scenery. See you all in 2 weeks!
Hey Congrats - and good luck on the fishing trip.  Don
congrats and hope you have a great time
Awsome!  And like T.J. said, GREAT honeymoon.
Hey Congrats and remember we want to see lots of pics of nice fish and we know your wife is good at fishing also.  Have a good Honeymoon.  MTP
Congrats on the married part... look forward to the pictures of one of the most beautiful places in the world!  Cheers,  Jen
Congrats and enjoy the honeymoon  Joey
Way to go Bud!Enjoy your honeymoon and get some fish.
You never really specified...is that with or without the wife  If it's with the wife shes a keeper for going fishing on the honeymoon.
congrats man! good luck with the honeymoon
congrats on your marriage... may the fish gods be with you for your honeymoon...
Congrats!  Good luck with the fishing.  Maureen
Attaboy Danbouk .. Congrats to you both.
Congrats!!!!  Hope you have an awesome time on your fishing trip!!!
Congrats and may you both have tight lines throughout your trip.
